  <summary date="2020-05-07T18:02:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Workers Banking Assistance Act

This bill provides additional criteria a federal financial supervisory agency may consider in its evaluation of a financial institution's community investment. Specifically, a financial institution's assistance to certain individuals affected by a federal government shutdown may be considered as part of such evaluation.</summary>
